message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to provide exceptional value. Given its quality and features, it's worth more than $80 to us. Considering the benefits it offers, we're extending an exclusive opportunity to you at a special introductory price of $95. This is an excellent chance to experience the product before it's available to the general public at a higher cost. Would you like to proceed with this offer?
